        #<Rarity Color Fix>

            #<Description>

                #NoMoreJebaited

                By Koby

                Vanilla: https://i.imgur.com/15e0qIR.jpg

                RarityColorFix: https://i.imgur.com/dB3sFHz.jpg

                Changes the rarity color of unique aftermarket items to a darker blue to be more distinguishable from normal rare guns.

                Also changes the color of Moxxi weapons to a blood red.

                Supports Gemstone weapons from the Unofficial Community Patch.

                Changes the order of items in the inventory.

                Pearl -> Seraph -> Legendary -> Moxxi -> Unique -> Gemstone -> E-Tech -> Very Rare...

                Full Filter Tool support!

                Thanks to Dave for providing the Rarity Colors resource.

                DISCLAIMER:

                This mod will most likely conflict with any mod which changes rarity colors.

            #</Description>

            #<Rarity Color Change>

                set WillowGame.GlobalsDefinition RarityLevelColors ((MinLevel=0,MaxLevel=0,Color=(B=175,G=193,R=205,A=0),DropLifeSpanType=DROP_ShortLived,RarityRating=RARITY_Unknown),(MinLevel=1,MaxLevel=1,Color=(B=255,G=255,R=255,A=255),DropLifeSpanType=DROP_ShortLived,RarityRating=RARITY_Common),(MinLevel=2,MaxLevel=2,Color=(B=11,G=210,R=61,A=255),DropLifeSpanType=DROP_LongLived,RarityRating=RARITY_Uncommon),(MinLevel=3,MaxLevel=3,Color=(B=255,G=142,R=60,A=255),DropLifeSpanType=DROP_LiveForever,RarityRating=RARITY_Rare),(MinLevel=4,MaxLevel=4,Color=(B=229,G=63,R=168,A=255),DropLifeSpanType=DROP_LiveForever,RarityRating=RARITY_VeryRare),(MinLevel=5,MaxLevel=5,Color=(B=0,G=180,R=255,A=255),DropLifeSpanType=DROP_LiveForever,RarityRating=RARITY_Legendary),(MinLevel=6,MaxLevel=6,Color=(B=168,G=0,R=202,A=255),DropLifeSpanType=DROP_LiveForever,RarityRating=RARITY_VeryRare),(MinLevel=7,MaxLevel=10,Color=(B=0,G=180,R=255,A=255),DropLifeSpanType=DROP_LiveForever,RarityRating=RARITY_Legendary),(MinLevel=12,MaxLevel=50,Color=(B=147,G=112,R=147,A=255),DropLifeSpanType=DROP_LiveForever,RarityRating=RARITY_VeryRare),(MinLevel=51,MaxLevel=60,Color=(B=163,G=128,R=70,A=255),DropLifeSpanType=DROP_LiveForever,RarityRating=RARITY_Rare),(MinLevel=61,MaxLevel=70,Color=(B=50,G=0,R=230,A=255),DropLifeSpanType=DROP_LiveForever,RarityRating=RARITY_Rare),(MinLevel=71,MaxLevel=80,Color=(B=0,G=180,R=255,A=255),DropLifeSpanType=DROP_LiveForever,RarityRating=RARITY_Legendary),(MinLevel=81,MaxLevel=90,Color=(B=184,G=154,R=255,A=255),DropLifeSpanType=DROP_LiveForever,RarityRating=RARITY_Seraph),(MinLevel=91,MaxLevel=170,Color=(B=255,G=255,R=0,A=0),DropLifeSpanType=DROP_LiveForever,RarityRating=RARITY_Unknown),(MinLevel=171,MaxLevel=175,Color=(B=71,G=71,R=207,A=255),DropLifeSpanType=DROP_ShortLived,RarityRating=RARITY_Unknown),(MinLevel=176,MaxLevel=180,Color=(B=167,G=199,R=255,A=0),DropLifeSpanType=DROP_ShortLived,RarityRating=RARITY_Unknown),(MinLevel=181,MaxLevel=499,Color=(B=13,G=255,R=255,A=0),DropLifeSpanType=DROP_ShortLived,RarityRating=RARITY_Unknown),(Min
